WEBVTT

00:07.294 --> 00:08.864
<i>Previously</i>
<i>on The Borgias...</i>

00:08.865 --> 00:10.603
<i>The sentence is banishment.</i>

00:10.604 --> 00:12.005
<i>Cardinal Versucci</i>
<i>will be stripped</i>

00:12.039 --> 00:13.573
<i>and his property</i>
<i>will be donated</i>

00:13.674 --> 00:16.473
<i>to our Holy Mother Church.</i>

00:16.507 --> 00:18.139
<i>Cardinal</i>
<i>Versucci was the last person</i>

00:18.206 --> 00:19.306
<i>in the room.</i>

00:19.374 --> 00:20.674
<i>No one can find him.</i>

00:20.741 --> 00:22.842
<i>May I introduce</i>
<i>Francesco Gonzaga,</i>

00:22.877 --> 00:24.276
<i>Duke of Mantua,</i>

00:24.311 --> 00:26.947
<i>and his bride,</i>
<i>the lovely Bianca.</i>

00:26.981 --> 00:28.314
Divine indeed.

00:28.382 --> 00:29.682
You know what I want.

00:29.750 --> 00:31.583
You wish your son
to be acknowledged.

00:31.651 --> 00:32.950
To separate a mother
from her child -

00:33.051 --> 00:34.218
Her bastard child.

00:34.286 --> 00:35.419
My feelings on that matter

00:35.487 --> 00:38.222
have already been made
abundantly clear.

00:38.290 --> 00:40.225
You sat there,
meek as a girl,

00:40.326 --> 00:42.227
and said not one word.

00:42.295 --> 00:43.896
<i>Catherina Sforza Riario,</i>

00:43.963 --> 00:45.565
<i>Countess of Forli.</i>

00:45.599 --> 00:49.035
We had almost lost hope
of having you kneel before us.

00:49.069 --> 00:50.470
<i>You invite her here?</i>

00:50.504 --> 00:53.507
<i>Into the heart of Rome onto</i>
<i>the steps of the Vatican</i>

00:53.575 --> 00:55.042
<i>for the whole world to see?</i>

00:55.143 --> 00:56.678
My invitation
of Catherina Sforza

00:56.712 --> 00:57.913
is a move in the game -

00:57.981 --> 01:00.516
<i>as is your marriage</i>
<i>to the pope's daughter.</i>

01:00.551 --> 01:01.884
<i>My marriage is no game.</i>

01:01.952 --> 01:03.886
<i>I love Lucrezia.</i>

01:03.921 --> 01:05.722
Who did this?

01:05.790 --> 01:07.090
Only my brother would've -

01:07.158 --> 01:08.726
Is this what I am
to your brother?

01:08.760 --> 01:10.194
A question mark?

01:10.228 --> 01:12.196
Is this what I am
to your family?

01:12.264 --> 01:13.997
I would confound this pope.

01:14.065 --> 01:15.699
<i>Our little pack of wolves.</i>

01:15.733 --> 01:17.267
<i>If they pledge</i>
<i>their swords to me,</i>

01:17.335 --> 01:19.369
<i>and the Borgia estates</i>
<i>I'll divide among them.</i>

01:21.372 --> 01:23.105
What on God's earth?

01:23.173 --> 01:25.074
Am I so hard to love?

01:25.108 --> 01:28.076
Only a Borgia, it seems,
can truly love a Borgia.

01:28.111 --> 01:29.478
Why deny ourselves the pleasure

01:29.545 --> 01:31.813
of which we're already accused?

01:36.918 --> 01:39.724
[♪]

